item.title: What is Wing Chun?
item.author: Max Tottenham,
item.description: What is Wing Chun? Wing Chun is a close quarters hand to hand combat system developed in Southern China which has recently gained popularity due to the martial arts film Ip Man released in 2008 which is loosely based on the life of the late grand master Ip Man.
